name: YING & YANG
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Balance male and female energies within and without.

Similar yet different. Complementing, supporting, each energy has its own amazing properties which when balanced lead to harmony and peace. Down to earth, the everyday, seeing each other warts and all. Real and mundane. Sometimes we can have fantastical visions of our partner, this card is about accepting them for who they are with all the flaws of being human. You each come to the relationship with your own set of luggage that is unique to you and part of getting to know each other is understanding your own baggage, knowing what is theirs and what is yours and not to project yours onto them.

You are in me and I am in you
You balance me and I balance you
These energies together harmonise life
I appreciate you and you appreciate me
You grow that which is great within you within me 
I grow that which is great within me 
within you.

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
